## 1. Product Overview

TrustScan is a native iOS application that empowers users to detect and understand digital scams by submitting screenshots of suspicious content for intelligent analysis. The application serves as a first-line defense tool, providing threat assessments, risk scores, contextual warnings, and actionable recommendations in response to content the user encounters in their daily digital life.

The application is the client-facing layer of a broader scam detection platform. All heavy analysis — including OCR processing, text extraction, URL sandboxing, threat scoring, and intelligence database lookups — is performed by a separate backend system. TrustScan's responsibility is to provide a trustworthy, intuitive, and reliable user experience that surfaces these insights clearly and empowers users to act with confidence.

The application targets iOS 16 and later, built with SwiftUI, and designed for iPhone as the primary form factor with iPad support.

