## 8. Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance

| ID | Requirement |
|----|-------------|
| NFR-01 | The application must launch to the home screen within 1.5 seconds on a supported device under normal conditions. |
| NFR-02 | The submission UI must respond to user interaction within 100ms. |
| NFR-03 | Loading states must appear within 200ms of a submission action to prevent perceived freezing. |
| NFR-04 | Image compression and preparation for upload must not block the main thread. |
| NFR-05 | History list must render 100+ entries without perceptible lag. |

